custom_css: @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {.desktop_screen.button-cta {display: none; } .mobile_screen.button-cta {display: flex; border-radius: 0; } .main-carousel-cta-btn {margin: auto; }}
.carousel-section-title-wrapper p {display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 20px;}
